data.description: LOOKING TO GET OFF THE GRID?!?!? Here is your chance! Not only do you get off the grid but you get to fish on your own part of the Kankakee River on nearly 10 Acres with River Frontage Access!! Not only that!!! You get a Main Residence a 2nd Separate Residence, Multiple Pole Barns, Utility Shed & Storage!! Definitely needs TLC & updating but once done this 3 Bed, 1 Bath Main Residence will become your sanctuary with an income property built-in or Related-Living, etc. The 2nd home has 1 Bed, 1 Bath and a garage underneath. Campers were allowed to use a portion of the property at one time so there is a separate-shower/bath structure also on the property! There are 3 pole barns, storage sheds, etc. on the property! This property also has it's own concrete dock/boat ramp. Last of it's kind that has been grandfathered in. So if you like to store multiple Vehicles, Boats, Snowmobiles, Motorcycles and More you definitely can do so here! SOLD AS-IS! Schedule your showing today!
